### Get all shops (default pagination)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/shops HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

### Get all shops (custom pagination)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/shops?_page=1&_limit=10 HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

### Get shop by id
GET http://localhost:5000/api/shops/4 HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

### Post shop
POST http://localhost:5000/api/shops HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Test post",
  "description": "",
  "url": "",
  "image": ""
}

### Put shop
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/shops HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 4,
  "title": "Test put",
  "description": "test description",
  "url": "http://domain.loc",
  "image": ""
}

### Delete shop
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/shops/4 HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json